    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚因通货膨胀飙升而增加警察和军队的工资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/nigeria-increases-pay-for-police-military-as-inflation-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚政府同意将包括警察、军事和情报人员在内的公务员工资提高35%，以应对这个西非国家不断上升的通货膨胀和严重的不安全局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/nigeria-increases-pay-for-police-military-as-inflation-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:39:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
